                but WITHOUT ANY WARRANTY; without even the implied warranty of<LineBreak/>
                MERCHANTABILITY or FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE.  See the<LineBreak/>
                GNU General Public License for more details.<LineBreak/>
